"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        Certificate objects with different sets of internal data.
        """
a = Certificate(certificate_type=self.certificate_type_a, certificate_value
    =self.certificate_value_a)
b = Certificate(certificate_type=self.certificate_type_b, certificate_value
    =self.certificate_value_b)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
